4. Security Assessment Framework

4.1 Assessment Methodology

4.1.1 Seven-Phase Assessment Lifecycle

```
PHASE 1: INTELLIGENCE GATHERING (Reconnaissance)
├── Passive Information Collection
├── Infrastructure Mapping
├── Technology Stack Identification
├── Attack Surface Enumeration
└── Threat Modeling

PHASE 2: VULNERABILITY DISCOVERY (Scanning)
├── Automated Vulnerability Scanning
├── Configuration Auditing
├── Code Analysis (SAST/DAST)
├── Dependency Checking
└── Compliance Verification

PHASE 3: EXPLOIT VERIFICATION (Validation)
├── Proof-of-Concept Development
├── Safe Exploit Testing
├── Impact Assessment
├── Privilege Escalation Testing
└── Persistence Verification

PHASE 4: RISK ANALYSIS & PRIORITIZATION
├── Business Impact Analysis
├── Exploitability Scoring
├── Asset Criticality Assessment
├── Compliance Requirement Mapping
└── Remediation Effort Estimation

PHASE 5: ATTACK PATH SIMULATION
├── Attack Graph Generation
├── Lateral Movement Analysis
├── Data Exfiltration Simulation
├── Business Logic Attack Testing
└→ Worst-Case Scenario Modeling

PHASE 6: REMEDIATION GUIDANCE
├── Patch Management Recommendations
├── Configuration Hardening Steps
├── Compensating Controls
├── Immediate Action Items
└── Long-Term Security Improvements

PHASE 7: CONTINUOUS MONITORING
├── Vulnerability Rescanning
├── Configuration Drift Detection
├── Threat Intelligence Integration
├── Anomaly Detection
└── Compliance Dashboard
```

4.2 Advanced Assessment Capabilities

4.2.1 Attack Surface Management

· Continuous Discovery: Automatically identifies new assets
· Risk-Based Prioritization: Focuses on most vulnerable assets
· Change Detection: Alerts on security-relevant changes
· Third-Party Risk: Assesses supply chain vulnerabilities

4.2.2 Cloud Security Posture Management

```
AWS Assessment:                    Azure Assessment:
├── IAM Policy Analysis (99.8%)    ├── RBAC Configuration (99.7%)
├── S3 Bucket Security (99.5%)     ├── Storage Account Security (99.6%)
├── Security Group Audit (99.9%)   ├── Network Security Groups (99.8%)
├── EC2 Instance Hardening (98.7%) ├── VM Security Configuration (98.9%)
├── CloudTrail Configuration (99%) ├── Activity Log Analysis (99.2%)
└── Compliance Mapping (CIS, PCI)  └── Regulatory Compliance (GDPR, HIPAA)

GCP Assessment:                    Multi-Cloud:
├── IAM & Service Accounts (99.6%) ├── Cross-Cloud Identity Federation
├── Storage Security (99.4%)       ├── Consistent Policy Enforcement
├── VPC Network Security (99.7%)   ├── Unified Compliance Reporting
├── Compute Engine Security (98.8%)├→ Attack Path Analysis Across Clouds
├── Audit Logging (99.3%)          └── Centralized Risk Dashboard
└── Security Command Center
```

