```
Key Metrics Displayed:
• Mean Time to Discovery (MTTD): <1 hour for critical vulnerabilities
• Mean Time to Remediation (MTTR): Actionable within 24 hours
• Vulnerability Density: Vulnerabilities per 1,000 lines of code
• Risk Exposure Score: 0-1000 scale with trend analysis
• Compliance Score: Percentage of requirements met
• Attack Surface Index: Quantitative measure of exposure
